    excerpt:
      "I roasted three whole heads of garlic for a Sunday pasta and the smell was still clinging to the dish towels two days later. After timing the methods that actually cleared the air against the ones that only spread the smell, here is the order that worked fastest and the mistakes that kept the garlic ghost hanging around until midweek.",
